emotes.msg: Ugh! I hate this stuff, but I have a friend who likes it. Maybe you should drop in on him.
Hmmm, I can't use a stamp... Oh! Very funny! Very funny! Get outta my house Mr. Funnyman!
What do you want me to do with this? Pick my teeth? Stop bothering me I have some serious drinking to do.
You find enough of this you might be able to have some tailor make a really fine shirt.
Hey. This is stolen property. I might swill my share of ale, but I'm not swilling my brew from Celcynd's mug.
Aw! None Left!
Ahem, I like my privacy when I can get it!
Rotten tourists.
You know, this isn't some vacation hotspot. This is my home!
Wipe your feet! Cleaning house takes time away from my life's endeavor.
Nothing you see here is for sale! Not even for...
How much did you say you had?
Hey, down here bozo!
I can't even see out the window!
This sucks!
Think they're so big! I'll show'em.
My boots don't fit anymore.
I can drink five times my weight in stout!
You don't want me angry with you. Most of my punches tend to land below the belt.
I can't decide. Do you think I should decorate in Neo-Aluvian or Classic Sho?
I'm looking for a growth spell. If you find one let me know.
You know what they say. Small something or other, big something something.
Did you notice that everything seems to have gotten larger?
Small am I? I could drink you under the table!
No, not drink under the table! You rasell frassin! Get out of here!
People are always coming up to me "Oh, look how cute! A little Ulgrim!"
Gits!
One advantage to my size is that all my stout mugs are bigger!
You know it's good when you have to stop and breathe.
Great! You found my Home Brew!
Ahh!!! If that ain't the mothers milk to me! I've been saving that stout for a special occasion like this one.
What special occasion? Why my coming home party of course!
Let's see, I think I have a reward for you here.
Don't say I never gave you anything!
No thanks, I never get hangovers. You keep it.
Wah Chon's winter brew!
Ulgrim tips the stein and drains it in one long draught.
Gasp! Great Mattekar that's tasty! This inspires me to rhyme!
A larger lager lather is the taste I'd rather gather
when my lesser lager's suds are in the drink.
Then I mull the flavor over with it's hops and malts and clover
and again about the pub is what I think.
What's this?
Hey! This is half of that spell I wrote!
Good thing I was able to find the other half. Now let's see...
A little here...
A little there...
There good as new... almost. Wow, this is a really good spell. Let me just copy this down...
Ulgrim crouches and writes the spell on the back of his hand.
Here...
I want you to have it. It won't be all that useful to you I'm afraid, but you never know. Just don't depend on it. I don't have anywhere to go, but the Big Guy travels around quite a bit.
Aha! Another ring for my collection.
Of course I already found the only ring I'll ever need, but thanks.
Aha! Another ring for my collection.
Wait, This ring looks familiar.
This is MY RING!!!
You stoles it!!!
Get out of my house you nasty thief!!!
Hey, good stuff, thanks. Tough to find this around here. What? You're standing there looking at me with your mouth open. You expect me to say something special for this? I'm not a performing monkey!
Expect me to drink this eh?
Ulgrim drinks the mead quickly.
Bleh! Too sweet, I prefer something a bit... stouter.
Ale? I don't drink water unless I have to.
But, I might have to so I'll just hold onto this.
Ptooey!
Ulgrim pours out the water.
Ulgrim crosses his arms and mutters something under his breath.
Never touch the stuff.
I just figured it out!
It was so simple. Now we can all go home!
Oh, what's this then? Red? Well...I'll try any drink once.
Do you hear that?
Oh, hello! Were you saying something?
I'm feeling particularly good today for some reason.
Well, glad you could stop by!
Well, it's nice and hot, but it's missing that little kick which makes it really good.
Let's see, just a bit of this stuff...
...and this is a perfect warm me up.
What? You want to know how to make this? No Way! It's a secret, get your own peppermint!
Ulgrim suddenly lurches to the side and spills his drink all over his shirtfront.
Oops.
Hey Peppermint! Have you tried my secret recipe?
Then try some of my Peppermint Pumpkin Pie!
Something doesn't smell quite right about this stuff. You got it from Jaleh's, eh? Well I've no love for the money grabbing b--. Say you don't think that I had anything to...
Well of all the insane ideas to pop into people's heads. Be off with you! I've better things to do than deal with some hack investigation.
Ulgrim swigs the brew.
Whew! Tangy. Yup, that was definitely not right. I feel kind of sleepy. You have any more Ale?
OswaldStep1
CoveOswaldUlgrim
Hey, since you're already bothering me you could at least make yourself useful and fetch me some of my home brewed stout from the basement.
Just take the portal to the lower basement and look for the glowing stout, you can't miss it. And don't go messing around with any of my things or I'll kick you in the shins!
